  "3030950": {
    "name": "Mooh",
    "steam_appid": 3030950,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3030950/extras/f265c02689063efc32b60d43b4f368ab.avif?t=1740761344\" width=616 height=230 /></span><br><br>在这款赛博朋克单人游戏中探索宇宙，一头小牛会让你头晕目眩。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3030950/extras/c877c8fe4d070c4ffe70aee0ea9f0a02.avif?t=1740761344\" width=616 height=140 /></span><br><br>关于外星人绑架牛的故事和城市传说层出不穷，但牛被绑架后会发生什么呢？<br>在一个和平的星球上，牛只会散步、吃草和放屁，一头无辜的牛被绑架到一个陌生的星球，并被囚禁。<br>逃脱后，它开始探索新世界，寻找回家的方法。<br>曾经只是牧场中另一头牛的存在，现在变成了一个有个性、恐惧和欲望的个体。<br>它的旅程不仅仅是发现其他世界：它是在发现自我。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3030950/extras/92260264a7fdb5a0a57d888494027f65.avif?t=1740761344\" width=616 height=140 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >360º 平台</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3030950/extras/071881fd8b2ecab60ce22c6404d1a3a6.poster.avif?t=1740761344\" width=616 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3030950/extras/071881fd8b2ecab60ce22c6404d1a3a6.webm?t=1740761344\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3030950/extras/071881fd8b2ecab60ce22c6404d1a3a6.mp4?t=1740761344\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>围绕整个星球移动，通过重力转换机制将天花板变为地面。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >修复飞船</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3030950/extras/c0c12713727f35cf5ba79d6eeca18239.poster.avif?t=1740761344\" width=616 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3030950/extras/c0c12713727f35cf5ba79d6eeca18239.webm?t=1740761344\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3030950/extras/c0c12713727f35cf5ba79d6eeca18239.mp4?t=1740761344\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>找到并收集修复破损飞船所需的部件，帮助角色离开那里。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >击败敌人并解决难题</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3030950/extras/da2fb5770344e970c07d01f889ad47c4.poster.avif?t=1740761344\" width=616 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3030950/extras/da2fb5770344e970c07d01f889ad47c4.webm?t=1740761344\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3030950/extras/da2fb5770344e970c07d01f889ad47c4.mp4?t=1740761344\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>每个星球都有不同的敌人需要击败和谜题需要解决。行动前请三思：可能是你最后的一步！<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >咪莫萨牛</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3030950/extras/1a449ae31c9b30211759758efdec182f.poster.avif?t=1740761344\" width=616 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3030950/extras/1a449ae31c9b30211759758efdec182f.webm?t=1740761344\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3030950/extras/1a449ae31c9b30211759758efdec182f.mp4?t=1740761344\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Mooh并不是唯一被绑架的牛！要拯救其他我们亲切称之为“咪莫萨”的牛，您需要找到它们被关押的牢房并将其释放。咪莫萨牛会作为旅行伙伴加入你在飞船中的冒险。<br>你救出的咪莫萨牛越多，你看到的不同皮肤就越多！<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >学习新技能</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3030950/extras/9987ce191d61331920c3927fc30d3017.poster.avif?t=1740761344\" width=616 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3030950/extras/9987ce191d61331920c3927fc30d3017.webm?t=1740761344\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br>在飞船中，Mooh可以学习帮助你探索下一个星球的新技能。大多数技能可以同时用于解决难题和攻击敌人。<br>随着每项技能的学习，Mooh会变得更加赛博朋克！",
